    <description>Proximal leaves with mostly 2- or 3-rayed trichomes adaxially. Flowers: petals
        usually yellow, rarely lavender or purplish. Fruits usually 4-angled, rarely latiseptate.
        Seeds 1.5–2(–2.4) × 0.7–1.2 mm; not winged. 2n = 36.</description>
